    <div class="padding-large bone">
        <b>beta 0.9</b>
        <ul>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Beginner Guide</b>: Added to the home screen, displayed until the player reaches 3MW of production.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Messages Redesign</b>: Improved functionality with unread badges visible for new messages.
