            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Wind Potential System</b>: Each new wind turbine is built at a location with a specific average wind speed. The best locations are taken first, so new turbines have progressively worse average wind speeds. The map's wind potential determines the number of good locations available. More information is available on the wiki.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Freeing Locations</b>: For wind and hydro facilities, dismantling or decommissioning frees the location, allowing new facilities to be built with the same potential.
