            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Upgrade System</b>: Technological upgrades are no longer automatically applied to all facilities. Players must upgrade each facility individually.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>New Profile Page</b>: Now accessible directly from the navbar. Tables for Power, Storage, and Extraction facilities list all active instances, with options to upgrade or dismantle specific instances for a cost.
