            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>CO2 Absorbtion</b>: Servers start with 5Mt of CO2 in the atmosphere. The carbon capture rate is now proportional to the atmospheric CO2 amount, similar to extraction facilities.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Construction Power</b>: Remains constant during the construction period.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Interactive Priority List</b>: redesigned, shows in blue the generation facilitiesand in red the consumptions.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Synchronized Completion</b>: Constructions and technologies now finish in sync with the game clock (every 30 seconds).
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Market Prices</b>: Set prices must be higher than -5/MWh.
            </li>
            <li class="li_padding">
                <b>Resource Market</b>: More reactive to changes.
